{"tid":789550,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角有個派傳單仔好慘","createTime":"2018-08-22T10:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T10:24:12.000Z","uid":113178,"like":56,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cdbcd421d93412db0062e2c156c11cded99893d9","tid":789550,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:28:54.000Z","msg":"啱啱我行緊去餐廳食嘢嗰時有個派傳單仔係咁想質張唔知乜嘢比我，話差一張，派埋呢張就收工，我係都唔收。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食咗兩個鐘飯之後又撞番佢又話差一張，派埋呢張就收工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n派咗兩個鐘都派唔出最後一張好陰公。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打係旺角做吓好心幫佢收工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37caf04f645212cebe8aa13b48db296aeba8109","tid":789550,"uid":135986,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"咁你唔攞埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0d7dffe3e5c5287454c473c60a9438f0a4654f","tid":789550,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:33:51.000Z","msg":"扔咗佢啦"},{"pid":"91b05b3f0d3bf0f79e3b25769bffa40f48835855","tid":789550,"uid":113178,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"f37caf04f645212cebe8aa13b48db296aeba8109","tid":789550,"uid":135986,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"咁你唔攞埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:33:51.000Z","msg":"我毒撚唔夠膽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8cc22576c5994f7c92b80ef0ac682b55458fb3","tid":789550,"uid":169048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:34:54.000Z","msg":"樓主遇到個係港仔咪好<br />\n上次遇到個又係咁講 大陸女人<br />\n捉要拉鳩住我<br />\n